You can't carry with kids stuff.

01:53:26.530 --> 01:53:28.530
There's no such thing as Zebo the clown.

01:53:28.530 --> 01:53:35.650
No way.

01:53:35.650 --> 01:53:41.850
I'll just eat dinner and rub, Josh.

01:53:41.850 --> 01:53:46.600
How can that burn so fast?

01:53:46.600 --> 01:53:51.610
Cigar smoke.

01:53:51.610 --> 01:54:15.300
Come on.

01:54:15.300 --> 01:54:19.250
Ouija, this is Josh.

01:54:19.250 --> 01:54:20.250
I'm...

01:54:20.250 --> 01:54:22.250
Josh, slow down.

01:54:22.250 --> 01:54:23.250
Tell me the truth.

01:54:23.250 --> 01:54:25.250
Did you call my house before

01:54:25.250 --> 01:54:27.250
and pretend you were Zebo?

01:54:27.250 --> 01:54:29.250
Whoa, what's the matter, Josh?

01:54:29.250 --> 01:54:30.250
You sound kind of scared.

01:54:30.250 --> 01:54:32.250
I'm not.

01:54:32.250 --> 01:54:33.250
Yeah, okay, okay.

01:54:33.250 --> 01:54:34.250
I'm scared.

01:54:34.250 --> 01:54:35.250
I was scared on the ride,

01:54:35.250 --> 01:54:37.250
and I'm really scared now.

01:54:37.250 --> 01:54:38.250
Was that you?

01:54:38.250 --> 01:54:39.250
I'm keeping a break.

01:54:39.250 --> 01:54:41.250
Why would I...?

01:54:41.250 --> 01:54:42.250
What was that?

01:54:42.250 --> 01:54:44.250
Was that you, Cassie?

01:54:44.250 --> 01:54:45.250
Put down the phone.

01:54:45.250 --> 01:54:48.250
Josh, we only have one phone.

01:54:48.250 --> 01:54:50.250
It's gotta be in your house.

01:54:50.250 --> 01:57:10.850
If you don't get me, what's that?

01:57:10.850 --> 01:57:12.850
Just to show there's no hard feelings?

01:57:12.850 --> 01:57:13.850
Cigars.

01:57:13.850 --> 01:58:19.010
It's the most fun when you're laughing in the dark.

01:58:19.010 --> 01:58:21.010
The end.

01:58:21.010 --> 01:58:24.010
So it was a crazy old guy all along.

01:58:24.010 --> 01:58:25.010
No way.

01:58:25.010 --> 01:58:27.010
He could have done that stuff in the house.

01:58:27.010 --> 01:58:31.010
Maybe the old guy was really Zebo's ghost.

01:58:31.010 --> 01:58:34.830
Yeah.

01:58:34.830 --> 01:58:35.830
So what do you think, Kristen?

01:58:35.830 --> 01:58:37.830
Is Zebo gonna pay you a visit tonight?

01:58:37.830 --> 01:58:39.830
Sorry, Kiki, I did it.

01:58:39.830 --> 01:58:41.830
I sat through the whole story and I'm okay.

01:58:41.830 --> 01:58:44.830
What do you say to that?

01:58:44.830 --> 01:58:46.830
I'd say that's a good thing,

01:58:46.830 --> 01:58:48.830
because we wouldn't want you having nightmares.

01:58:48.830 --> 01:58:52.140
One win!

01:58:52.140 --> 01:59:01.820
Being a jerk.

01:59:01.820 --> 01:59:48.180
Thanks for watching. Nick takes over.

01:59:48.180 --> 01:59:49.180
Us!

01:59:49.180 --> 01:59:52.030
It's a great time.

01:59:52.030 --> 01:59:53.030
Taking over the school.

01:59:53.030 --> 01:59:55.030
Slimeing everyone and everything.

01:59:55.030 --> 01:59:56.030
Dancing with Kris Kross.

01:59:56.030 --> 01:59:58.030
And it all happened because I sent in a postcard.

01:59:58.030 --> 02:00:00.030
So keep watching the place where only kids win.

